enhanced_by.reason: The add method populates the hResults map, which is used by getResultValueMap to retrieve validation results.
The merge method combines results into hResults, which is also used by getResultValueMap.
The getValidatorResult method retrieves specific results from hResults, similar to how getResultValueMap retrieves and processes results.
The getPropertyNames method returns a set of keys from hResults, which is similar to the keys processed by getResultValueMap.
